OL,6,FITV News reporters Cari Davies and Amy
OL,7,FLewis have the latest after Martyn
OL,8,FBlake, the firearms officer who shot
OL,9,Fand killed Chris Kaba, is found not
OL,10,Fguilty of murder
OL,12,FThe family of Chris Kaba have said
OL,13,Fthey have been left with the "deep
OL,14,Fpain of injustice" after a jury found
OL,15,Fthe firearms officer who fatally shot
OL,16,Fhim not guilty of murder.
OL,18,FMartyn Blake, 40, stood trial at the
OL,19,FOld Bailey for shooting the 24-year-
OL,20,Fold in Streatham in September 2022,
OL,21,Fthrough the windscreen of his car.
