OL,6,FKayza Rose of the Justice for Chris
OL,7,FKaba Campaign said they will continue
OL,8,Fto fight for justice "until our last
OL,9,Fbreath"
OL,11,F"No family should endure the
OL,12,Funimaginable grief we have faced.
OL,13,FChris was stolen from us, and this
OL,14,Fdecision shows his life - and many
OL,15,Fothers like him - does not matter to
OL,16,Fthe system. Our son deserved better."
OL,18,FHis family's statement went on to
OL,19,Fexpress those who had stood beside
OL,20,Fthem since his killing, and said they
OL,21,F"will not be silenced".
