OL,6,F"We will continue fighting for Chris,
OL,7,Ffor justice, and for real change.
OL,8,FChris' life mattered, and nothing can
OL,9,Ftake that away from us," they added.
OL,11,FThe Justice for Chris Kaba Campaign
OL,12,Fechoed the family's words calling the
OL,13,Fverdict a "devastating moment" for the
OL,14,Fnation.
OL,16,FIn a statement, Temi Mwale and Kayza
OL,17,FRose said: "For the Kaba family,
OL,18,Fjustice was never just about a
OL,19,Fconviction - it's about systemic
OL,20,Fchange, a fight we will not abandon as
OL,21,Fa campaign.
