OL,6,F"Martyn Blake's acquittal is painful
OL,7,Fproof that our lives are not valued by
OL,8,Fthis system."
OL,10,FBody-worn camera footage shows the
OL,11,Fmoment Chris Kaba was fatally shot by
OL,12,FMartyn Blake
OL,14,FThe car Mr Kaba was driving had been
OL,15,Fused as a getaway vehicle in a
OL,16,Fshooting in nearby Brixton the night
OL,17,Fbefore, and was followed when a police
OL,18,Fofficer recognised the number plate.
OL,19,FOfficers did not know who was driving
OL,20,Fthe car at the time.
