OL,6,FMetropolitan Police Commissioner Sir
OL,7,FMark Rowley praised Mr Blake for
OL,8,Facting with "professionalism and
OL,9,Fdignity" in the years since the
OL,10,Fshooting, and said he was proud of the
OL,11,Fwork carried out by firearms officers.
OL,13,FHe said: "Today's verdict is
OL,14,Fsignificant. No firearms officer sets
OL,15,Fout on duty intent on ending a life -
OL,16,Ftheir sole purpose is the complete
OL,17,Fopposite, the protection and
OL,18,Fpreservation of life.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
