OL,6,F"Armed officers bravely intervened,
OL,7,Fnot knowing the risks they were about
OL,8,Fto face.
OL,10,F"Sergeant Blake made a split second
OL,11,Fdecision, based on what he thought was
OL,12,Fnecessary to protect his colleagues
OL,13,Fand protect London."
OL,15,FSir Mark went on to criticise the
OL,16,Fsystems used to hold police officers
OL,17,Fwho take lethal shots to account.
