OL,6,FMetropolitan Police Commissioner Sir
OL,7,FMark Rowley said called the system
OL,8,Fholding police to account is "broken"
OL,9,Fin response to the jury's verdict
OL,11,F"No police officer is above the law,
OL,12,Fbut we have been clear that the system
OL,13,Fholding police to account is broken,"
OL,14,Fhe said.
