OL,6,F"I worry about the lack of support
OL,7,Fofficers face for doing their best,
OL,8,Fbut most of all, I worry for the
OL,9,Fpublic. The more we crush the spirit
OL,10,Fof good officers, the less they can
OL,11,Ffight crime that risks London becoming
OL,12,Fless safe."
OL,14,FThe jury of nine men and three women
OL,15,Fwas told by prosecutor Tom Little KC
OL,16,Fthat Blake had misjudged the risk to
OL,17,Fhis colleagues, and had aimed for Mr
OL,18,FKaba's head when taking the fatal shot.
