OL,6,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper said she
OL,7,Frecognised the distress caused to Mr
OL,8,FKaba's family and concern brought by
OL,9,Fthe incident for communities and
OL,10,Fpolice officers - but urged the jury's
OL,11,Fconclusion to be respected.
OL,13,FShe said: "Criminal prosecutions
OL,14,Fbrought against police officers for
OL,15,Factions taken in the course of their
OL,16,Fduties are extremely rare. Each day,
OL,17,Fpolice officers across the country
OL,18,Fwork hard with bravery and integrity
OL,19,Fto keep the public safe.
