OL,6,FMayor of London Sadiq Khan sent his
OL,7,F"heartfelt sympathies" to Mr Kaba's
OL,8,Ffamily and pledged to continue to hold
OL,9,Fthe Metropolitan Police to account.
OL,11,F"I understand the impact Chris Kaba's
OL,12,Fdeath has had on London's communities
OL,13,Fand the anger, pain and fear it has
OL,14,Fcaused," he said.
OL,16,F"There's clearly still a wider lack of
OL,17,Ftrust in the police, particularly
OL,18,Fwithin the Black community, that needs
OL,19,Fto be addressed."
